export const colors = {
    extraDarkBlue: "#212A3A",
    darkBlue: "#32425C",
    blackBlue: "#293449",
    basicRed: "#ee3643",
    basicGreen: "#63a63E",
    activeBasicRed: "#cc3333",
    white: "#ffffff",
    basicGrey: "#c5c5c5",
    basicYellow: "#FFD180",
    activeBlackBlue: "#1d2739",
    black: "#000000",
}

export const container = {
    width: "940px",
    margin: "0 auto",
}

export const visuallyHidden = {
    position: "absolute",
    width: "1px",
    height: "1px",
    margin: "-1px",
    border: "0",
    padding: "0",
    whiteSpace: "nowrap",
    clipPath: "inset(100%)",
    clip: "rect(0 0 0 0)",
    overflow: "hidden"
}

export const newElementCatalog = {
    backgroundColor: colors.basicRed,
    height: "70px",
    width: "70px",
    position: "absolute",
    clipPath: "polygon(68% 0, 100% 32%, 100% 100%, 0 0)",
    left: "calc(100% - 70px)",
    backgroundImage: "url(/images/icons/new.svg)",
    backgroundRepeat: "no-repeat",
    backgroundPosition: "75% 25%"
}
